race.comment: COME ON GLAMOUR (1) registered a strong win at Ballina before leading again and beaten a nose in a CL3 over 1000m at Port Macquarie. Has a handy 2kg claim today and will jump and run from the inside gate. Keeps improving and should have them covered. MUM KNOWS (10) led and won her Maiden here first-up, but has been plainer the two since. Morgan is engaged today, and that's a positive. He's likely to push forward and the shorter sprint suits. LOVE 'N' ROCKETS (2) resumes and has switched from the top Brisbane stable. Has pieces of form that more than stack up and has trialled well at Grafton. The 2kg claimer has to manage the outside barrier but he should be running into it. MARTINDALE DANCER (7) can build on her 50 win at Bowraville.
